article_metadata.description: Before venturing out this week to meet with someone who can help you sign up for coverage through healthcare.gov, a little homework is in order. Give careful thought to your monthly budget and get a handle on the maximum amount that you could pay per month for a healthcare policy, said Raymonia Lacy, a patient "navigator" with the Ohio Association of Free Clinics.
